		"Name": "Partisan Heavy Rifle Tank",
		"Details": "Not designed or built by Kallon Industries, the Periphery Partisan is a mish-mash of roles for a tank chassis typically used for aera denial of aerospace units.  Armmed primiarly with 3 Heavy Rifles in two different configurations, the Periphery Partisan serves in both an anti mech formations as well as Anti Air Formations.   Two of the three Heavy Rifles are equiped with Revolver reloaders to increase rate of fire, with a downside of lower reliablity.  The center barrel however is instead fitted with enhanced stabalization gear to make it more accurate while shooting on the move.  This weird homoginization across the primary armarment leads to some intersting gunnery profiles. Additionally, it carries twin Machine Guns for defence against infantry.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Tracked: High traction, agile turning.</color></b>\n\n \n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 3/5 Hex: 90/150 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       130     40\n<b>Left</b>          90     40\n<b>Right</b>        90     40\n<b>Rear</b>         80     40\n<b>Turret</b>      114     40\n\n<b>Total</b>      504    200\n",
		"Icon": "Partisan"
	},
